snippet.title: Duke Dashington Trailer
snippet.description:
NOW AVAILABLE IN APP STORE: https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/id904740787?mt=8

Do you have what it takes to be the fastest treasure hunter in the world? Duke Dashington is a fast-paced puzzle platformer with simple touch controls and over 100 levels of platforming across 4 vastly different temples! Rush for the treasures before the ceiling collapses on you!

Soon available on App Store on 4th of September! Android version is also in works.
